sequenceDiagram
    participant C1 as Client A (Author)
    participant E as Express API
    participant MS as MessageService
    participant D as PostgreSQL (Prisma)
    participant SM as SocketManager (Socket.IO)
    participant C2 as Client B (Recipient)

    C1->>E: POST /api/messages (content, channelId)
    E->>MS: sendMessage(userId, channelId, content)
    MS->>D: message.create({ data })
    D-->>MS: New Message Object
    MS->>SM: getIO().to(serverId).emit('message:received')
    SM-->>C2: Event 'message:received' (Real-time)
    MS-->>E: New Message Data
    E-->>C1: Response 201 { success: true, data }